reproducibilityReceipt.Rd

Insert git repository and R session info into Rmarkdown documents. Based on suggestions in a Twitter thread by Miles McBain (https://twitter.com/MilesMcBain/status/1263272935197782016?s=20).

Arguments

title

Header title for the inserted details section.
